    "7211412": {
        "Desc": "Activate the Kamuijima Cannons and destroy the rifts",
        "Tips": "Open your inventory to view the Kamuijima Cannon Map",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "The Fatui... What are they doing here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is it that you're doing in Inazuma?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Well, I came to Inazuma with the consultant team. In truth, I'm just your everyday engineer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "To be honest, my real reason for being here was to shoot a \"dokumentari film\" on-site at the Mikage Furnace for the purpose of promoting our nation's technologies."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "But seeing the furnace's current state, I think it's best if I didn't shoot that film..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What is Fontaine like?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "#Ah, my fine {F#lass}{M#lad}, that's a splendiferous question!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Indeed, I often ask myself how I might describe the charm of my country to others, even with my limited knowledge and vocabulary."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Now, what should I speak of first?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "For instance, I could tell you of the majestic waterfall that made a deep impression on my soul as I worked in my study in Petrichor."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Or perhaps I could sing the praises of the countless gorgeous maidens in the Court of Fontaine, ethereal as the clouds themselves..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Or the mesmerizing lake that held the reflections of the stars and the moon, such that walking along its banks was like treading amid the celestial skies..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You really do love Fontaine, don't you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Of course! And I shall tell you more about its wonders once I've found a satisfactory answer to that question of mine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are these \"films\" that you were talking about?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Oh, that? It's something that I discovered when I was researching Kameras."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "I made some improvements to the Kamera and turned it into a Film Kamera that is also capable of continuously projecting a string of photos, thus creating moving images."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "This technique is still in its preliminary stages and is far from perfect, so I have yet to formally apply for a patent. Not that I really could apply at this point in my current circumstances..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "But before I left Fontaine, I heard that some of my colleagues were quite interested in this act of playing back images in sequence... *sigh* I can only hope that they don't act all too quickly..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
