    "7211801": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Finally! At long last, it is done! Fortunately, I remember these specifications..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So, we're going in to purify the Tatarigami energy, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Well, as much as I would love to get in there and wrap this up, we must not act so rashly when faced with the Tatarigami."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Moreover, some of the required materials I simply could not find, so I had to make do with some last-minute substitutions. The result being that the reliability of this device is somewhat..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Hmm. Well, let me just say that \"in some circumstances, it may not achieve the desired efficacy.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "It can be used normally just fine, yes, but I doubt that it can withstand any accidents. The slightest jolt will likely knock some of the components out of place..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "As such, we still require a little more preparation before we can put our new friend here to work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "I'd like you to go near the Mikage Furnace and record some data for me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Consider it done."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Thank you very much. I'll be waiting for you here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do we really need to be so cautious?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Of course we do. To tell you the truth, I'm already cutting out quite a few steps here compared to the proper protocol. If Mr. Flois were here, it would be another week before we'd finish working through his process."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Anyway, desperate times call for desperate measures, and as representative of the project review panel, technically this is my call... so, I hereby authorize us to adapt our approach to suit the situation."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7211802": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Xavier",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "I wonder if Inazuma did appointed a project manager for this whole Mikage Furnace business..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7211803": {
        "Desc": "Take a picture of the situation at the Mikage Furnace",
        "Tips": "Use the photo-taking function to take a picture of the Mikage Furnace's storage devices and smelting facilities",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "So, have you scouted the situation out?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That I have."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7211804": {
        "Desc": "Take a picture of the situation at the Mikage Furnace",
        "Tips": "Use the photo-taking function to take a picture of the Mikage Furnace's storage devices and smelting facilities",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Great! Let me see..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "We're in luck, it seems. The Mikage Furnace is quite stable, and the energy within is not yet over-saturated."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "At this level of concentration, my device will still hold out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Do we need to purify all that energy?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "If this device could do that, why, I would have applied for a patent long ago. But our fine friend here can only decrease the energy level in a localized area."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "However, the reason for the deactivation of the Mikage Furnace and the failure of even its auto-restart program is the high saturation of Tatarigami energy."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "As long as we find the area with the highest concentration and purify it, we should be able to restart the core."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "At that point, the Mikage Furnace should restart, and beyond that point, any further issues will not be our concern."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "That's the plan. But before we execute it, I still have a few final preparations to make."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
